<a href="#video-link" data-video-id="7pwohw" data-video-descrip="Paradise Lose &amp;amp; Overly Sarcastic Production portray Satan, with his rebellion and turn from God being driven, by his envy for Jesus &amp;amp; his father." data-video-title="Paradise Lost's Satan" data-video-url="https://d1w6li7s85ibls.cloudfront.net/qvbr/7pwohw_640x360p_qvbr.mp4" data-video-thumbnail="https://static.tvtropes.org/trope_videos_transcoded/images/sd/screen_shot_2020_05_11_at_100050_am.png" data-video-trope="Main/DrivenByEnvy" data-video-tropename="Driven by Envy" data-video-approval="APPROVED" data-video-troper-rating="" data-video-average-rating="5.00" data-video-rating-count="7" data-video-media-sources="Literature/ParadiseLost,WebAnimation/OverlySarcasticProductions" class="video-launch-link video-overlay-link featured-widget-vid">
<div class="featured-widget-vid-iframe">
<video id='featured-video-player' class='video-js vjs-default-skin vjs-16-9' controls data-setup='{"ga": {"eventsToTrack": ["error"]}}'>
</video>
</div>
</a>
<h2 class="bold font-l">Paradise Lost's Satan</h2>
<p class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
Paradise Lose &amp; Overly Sarcastic Production portray Satan, with his rebellion and turn from God being driven, by his envy for Jesus &amp; his father. </p>
<p class='example_row'>Example of:<br><a href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/DrivenByEnvy" class='trope-example-link'>Driven by Envy</a></p>
</div>
<div class="video-examples-thumbs">
<a href="#video-link" data-video-id="z4ni3l" data-video-descrip="Red from Overly Sarcastic Productions, talks about Paradise Lost, and how it was one of the main reasons, behind Satan's shift from a demonic looking monster, to the more attractive, human version that are more common these days." data-video-title="OSP - Satan" data-video-url="https://d1w6li7s85ibls.cloudfront.net/qvbr/z4ni3l_640x360p_qvbr.mp4" data-video-thumbnail="https://static.tvtropes.org/trope_videos_transcoded/images/sd/z4ni3l.jpg" data-video-trope="Main/DracoInLeatherPants" data-video-tropename="Draco in Leather Pants" data-video-approval="APPROVED" data-video-troper-rating="" data-video-average-rating="" data-video-rating-count="" data-video-media-sources="WebAnimation/OverlySarcasticProductions,Literature/ParadiseLost" class="video-launch-link video-overlay-link video-background-image lazy-image" data-src="https://static.tvtropes.org/trope_videos_transcoded/images/sd/z4ni3l.jpg">
<p><span class="bold">OSP - Satan</span></p>
</a>
</div>
</div>
</div>
